Package mdlc

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coordinate
    Defines the position of each cell in a maze as a coordinate consisting of a row and a column
    Description
    This class encapsulates the maze description, read from the MDL file
    Generator
    This class is responsible for compiling the maze and generating the output
    MDLC
    This is the main class handling all command-line arguments and calling other appropriate functions to compile the maze
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Direction
    Defines the direction of movement for paths defined as direction-strings
    Mode
    Defines the output mode for the compiler
    SquareType
    Defines the type of a cell in a maze
    VisitDirection
    Defines the shape of the line drawn to indicate the visited-path
